title: Kyle's Quest Collection
description:
In this collection you will find Kyle's Quest V1 and six playable levels, Kyle's Quest 2 with just a couple playable levels.

Level editors for both versions of the game, so you can create your own levels.

I've also included two other games from Crimson Fire, Kyle's Quest Dungeon and Solskia.

All games are cracked and do not need to be registered.

Note: I didn't create any of this content, just scoured the web and pulled it all together for my own enjoyment, and decided that I'd bundle it up so you can play and enjoy it without having to search all over to find the games.
